category: Lua
requires: lua54
sdesc: "Mediator lua: Event Management for Clean & Decoupled Code"
ldesc: "mediator_lua allows you to subscribe and publish to a central object so
you can decouple function calls in your application. It's as simple as
mediator:subscribe(channel, function). Supports namespacing,
predicates, and more.
"
